ciJson is a JSON parsing and creating utility for Cinder.
It wraps JsonCpp. The block introduces some convenience 
methods while fully supporting JsonCpp's native syntax. 
This is cross platform except for the "saveUrl" method, 
which uses Windows' Internet API.

Sample code and project details here:
http://bantherewind.com/cijson

More about JsonCpp:
http://jsoncpp.sourceforge.net/

WISH LIST

- Sample project (VC10 + XCode)
- Single "load" and "save" methods which can take
  a filepath or URL, for Mac or Windows

